<ENAMEX TYPE="LAW">The Tax Reform Act</ENAMEX> of <ENAMEX TYPE="DATE">1986</ENAMEX> , which eliminated many tax shelters peddled by planners , and the stock market crash <ENAMEX TYPE="DATE">the next year</ENAMEX> did cause a sharp slump in such demand , and many planners had to make an unplanned exit from the business .
